  { id: "needs",       word: "needs",       group: 1, strap: "Conditions required to live well", desc: "Needs are the conditions required for people and communities to live with dignity. Some are immediate--food, water, shelter, safety--while others sustain longer-term well-being: care, belonging, meani" +
