  { id: "forms",       word: "forms",       group: 4, strap: "Structures that order and affect life", desc: "Forms are the structures and patterns that give order to what we encounter. They operate as systems of organisation--geometries, typologies, layouts--but also carry force in how they move, attract, or" +
