  { id: "ecologies",   word: "ecologies",   group: 4, strap: "Relations that sustain and transform life", desc: "Ecologies are interdependent systems through which forms and lives connect. They are not single entities but webs of relations linking elements through flows of energy, material, and meaning.\n\nIn na" +
