  { id: "stakeholders",word: "stakeholders",group: 5, strap: "Those who hold an interest or stake", desc: "Stakeholders are those with a recognised interest in the outcome of a project, decision, or system. A stake may be direct--financial, professional, personal--or indirect, such as environmental impact," +
