  { id: "coalitions",  word: "coalitions",  group: 5, strap: "Alliances formed around shared cause", desc: "Coalitions are alliances of actors who come together to pursue a common goal. They may be temporary or enduring, formal or informal, small or broad.\n\nThey often form when individual efforts are insu" +
